    <h3 class="aboutHeader">How to apply for ThinQ.tv internships OR Become a Volunteer
    </h3 ><br>
    <div class="livestreamInfo">
      <h3>&emsp;The first step to coming onboard at ThinQ.tv is to ATTEND THE LIVE INFO SESSION: </h3><br>
      <h4>
      - Tuesdays at 6:30pm Pacific Daylight Time (9:30pm Eastern Daylight Time) for UX/UI interns, Ruby on Rails interns, and open-source designers & developers.<br>
      - Thursdays at 5:30pm PDT / 8:30pm EDT for Leadership or Marketing internships and volunteer positions<br>
      </h4>

      Join the info Conversation by clicking <%= link_to 'Join Conversation', "https://crowdpublishtv.herokuapp.com/lisa", :class => "btn btn-lg btn-primary", :style => "border-radius:10px;"%> here or on the ThinQ.tv home page at the time designated for the involvement you're interested in for both our Scottsdale team or our remote team. <br>
